Like chris said it sounds like an electrical noise problem. See if you can
get your district's electricians out to check out the wiring. The lighting
and audio system should be on two separate circuits. Also check to see if
your amplifiers and your sound board are on the same circuit. That will make
a difference. In theory both circuits should have power
isolators/conditioners on them.

